Allison.Callery: Project concerns a road from Chingola to Kasumbalesa in the Copperbelt province. There is no GeoNameID for Kasumbalesa. The road segment Ndola-Mufulira-Mwambashi is in the Copperbelt Province and there is no GeoNameID for Mwambashi. It also includes the segement between Mufulira and Mokambo. There is no GeoNameID for Mokambo. The road segment from Kafulafuta to Luanshya is in the Copperbelt Province.
